## Key Design Decisions

- **Grade tuning uses weighted `tierBoost`, NOT fixed probability branching** — preserves deterministic seed behavior. Same keyword always produces the same grades.
- **Display safety over input mutation** — React JSX auto-escapes text, so user input stays intact. No `dangerouslySetInnerHTML` used anywhere.
- **Secondary `rng()` nudge** adds ±0.04 smoothing to tier boundaries, preventing hard jumps between grade bands.
